content.text: - Phase Space Analysis: 3D semantic space with determination, stability, and entropy dimensions - Topological Attractors: Eight knowledge types that classify information naturally - Trajectory Analysis: Track semantic evolution of concepts over time - Dynamic Modeling: Cognitive space that "breathes" to model knowledge boundaries - Visualization: 3D plotting capabilities for phase space exploration
